  m_Name: Day 6 Call 5 Seth
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - NewSpeakerName: 3
    dialogue: "Hey pal! It\u2019s Seth! Man, I just wanted to say that you\u2019ve
      made a huge impact on me over the past while. Sure, it\u2019s the others who\u2019ve
      been giving me pep talks and the like, but it\u2019s you that\u2019s been helping
      me find who I need to get through some tough times."
  - NewSpeakerName: 3
    dialogue: "Sometimes, I can have a hard time believing in myself, but because
      of all you\u2019ve helped me with, things don\u2019t really seem as bleak as
      they used to. I\u2019m happy to keep fixing stuff for the town. So thanks,
      really."
